{"tid":1884702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話撚左左膠唔撚係同路人架啦 大撚把手足買唔到口罩 泛民左膠就專派比藍絲廢老 連警察宿舍都走去派 後生仔呢？","createTime":"2020-02-17T18:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T05:04:34.000Z","uid":252492,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"919fabf74f82dd0c91e74d74bd6e448d068b769a","tid":1884702,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjYU073.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjYU073.jpg&h=5acc480d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃絲後生手足 泛民大愛左膠就叫你地食蕉啦<br />\n咪撚阻佢地拿光環<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母閪 選舉班廢老會投你地泛民咩<br />\n你地顛撚完未 個個等睇藍絲有報應<br />\n原本可以指撚住佢地黎笑 你就將黃絲勢力買返黎口罩一車車送比藍絲<br />\n結果自己黃色陣營都無口罩用比藍絲指鳩住黎笑<br />\n做藍絲根本無後果 又有政府 又有大愛左膠食哂兩邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"9ca106ebd568a1d8a150a861158f59fae234bf5a","tid":1884702,"uid":59976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/2856/1*LLGOhCPJU3kJdqSIX7qR2g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F2856%2F1%2ALLGOhCPJU3kJdqSIX7qR2g.png&h=07b0f9b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6c0b7e8e59a4a649a6e516a138c77134b562b3c","tid":1884702,"uid":252492,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:56:12.000Z","msg":"經典回顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃竹杭區議員民主黨徐遠華於rb前打卡後主動清除<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7144934/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7144934%2Fpage%2F1&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=6ad07dc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7144934/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MteAMOc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.